</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="7120FC623527BFB21859CC17F46FCF52" lastPageId="48" lastPageNumber="49" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" type="paratypes">
<paragraph id="0F1A372264D4543D4D5FD50DCD831525" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Paratypes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5417BE8AFA6592EA713C1DEA87281BF5" lastPageId="48" lastPageNumber="49" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
HI: Maui, Haleakala N.P., Kipahulu west rim ESE Kuiki, sifting 
<taxonomicName id="191AAC04683FE396551D1BD92CBEAB45" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Metrosideros" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Metrosideros" order="Myrtales" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Metrosideros</taxonomicName>
litter, 1830 m el., 12-v-1998 lot 08, Liebherr/Medeiros (CUIC, 
