), Kekuewa Hill 0.7 km N Puu Ahulili, sifting humus/moss, 1600 m el., 16-v-1998 lot 02 (CUIC, 1), lot 03 (CUIC, 1), Kaapahu, 1250 m el., 7-iv-2004 lot 01, 
<normalizedToken id="FE1A663CF99820C0C29E7702503D6E08" originalValue="Kaholoa‘a">Kaholoa'a</normalizedToken>
